[Redacted] will
send script to enable auto-batch.

Update: Per [Redacted], will update
script and re-run Userinit.

The issue is that in the Shift4
Payments config tool, if you do a
UserInit on any UTG2 settings, it
reverts any changes made in the
'advanced' settings, including:
-Auto Close
- Auto Close Hour
- Skip Shift4 PostAuth
This causes the system to ask for
tip/total adjustment after every
transaction processed.
